SUMMARY:Spike Sikes and the Get Real Gone at Cloverdale Arts Alliance
DESCRIPTION:The Cloverdale Arts Alliance is pleased to welcome Spike Sikes and the Get Real Gone to THE Jazz Club! \nSpike Sikes’ latest project has burst onto the Sonoma County jazz scene on the heels of the release of their 2025 self-titled album\, Spike Sikes and the Get Real Gone. Featuring Ray Fernandez on saxophone\, Dylan Juhan on bass\, and Mingo Lewis\, Jr. on percussion\, this quartet brings blues\, soul\, and swing to their “dirty jazz” vibe.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/spike-sikes-and-the-get-real-gone-at-cloverdale-arts-alliance/
LOCATION:Cloverdale Arts Alliance Gallery\, 204 N. Cloverdale Blvd\, Cloverdale\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
