SUMMARY:March Madness Solo Artists at The California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Three solo artists. One electric night. March Music Madness brings bold voices and unforgettable live sets.\nMarch Music Madness: Solo Artists showcases three distinct performers taking the stage for an evening of powerful\, personal\, and dynamic live music. Each set highlights the artistry and individuality of a single voice and instrument\, creating an intimate and high-impact listening experience. \nThe night features:\nJuke Tannins from 7–7:45pm\nChristopher Alexander from 8–8:45pm\nKerry Fogarty from 9–9:45pm. \nCatch one set or settle in for the full night of original sounds and inspired performances! \nTickets $12 in advance\, $18 at the door. Doors open 6:30pm.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/march-madness-solo-artists/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/March-Madness-Solos-2-1.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
