SUMMARY:Winter Book Sale by Friends of the Santa Rosa Libraries
DESCRIPTION:Fundraising for Santa Rosa libraries (Central\, Northwest\, Rincon Valley & Roseland) and Sonoma County History & Genealogy Library. THOUSANDS of GENTLY USED BOOKS DVDs CDs PUZZLES GAMES and more. Most items $2 or less\, and most children’s books are $1!\n– HOSTED by Friends of the Santa Rosa Libraries. All proceeds benefit Santa Rosa Libraries.\n– RESTOCKED DAILY & SOMETHING FOR EVERYONE! \nDATES/HOURS:\n– Friday March 6 Members-only Preview ($10 membership available at the door) 10 am – noon\, Open to the Public noon – 5:30pm\n– Saturday March 7 10am – 5:30pm\n– Sunday March 8 1pm – 4:30pm\nPAYMENT: Credit\, debit\, cash\, check and Apple\, Google\, Samsung Pay\nSee our ad in BOOKSALEFINDER.COM and Like us on Facebook (Friends of the Santa Rosa Libraries).
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/winter-book-sale-by-friends-of-the-santa-rosa-libraries-2/
