SUMMARY:Art Reception: "Renewal" ...with live music!
DESCRIPTION:Raising our minds and hearts by honoring the healing and sustaining power of art\, for each person and for society. \n22 artists of Sonoma County Art Trails featured. Come explore! Join us on the First Friday of March\, for a Meet the Artists reception\, from 5-7pm. \nThe evening will also be highlighted by LIVE MUSIC! One of the talented young cellists of Santa Rosa Symphony’s Youth Orchestra will play a few selections at about 6pm. Don’t miss it!
